tip.text: Super busy! Friendly staff and good and simple food! Clams, nails and 3 pepper steak are very good!!

tip.text: Awful, this place isn't for foodies or anyone who really appreciate food. A macchiato is served in a mug!! Eggs Benedict are served with oranges, grapes and melon... hot salsa is provided next to it.

Love this place, try the anchovies ramen dipping or the evil Princess of Darkness

tip.text: Well, Mama Mexicana should come back to the kitchen. The guacamole tastes like crinkly cardboard and wood paste.
